TextBody:
Hello,

If possible can you update further to server 5.9.4.1 and client 6.2.4.2?
Please let me know if you are already on 5.9.4.1 but only see the 6.2.4.1 client.

Is the OPT created for devices or for CAP policy?
If it is for the device, please select the device on the Epp client before adding the OTP.
IF it is for the CAP, please click on the CAP ta before adding the OTP.

Kind regards
__________________
Andrei Pop | Technical Support Engineer
Netwrix Endpoint Protector

Can you please import the offline patch below then download and install the Epp client 6.2.4.2?
http://download.endpointprotector.com/offline_agent_patches/MP-HWA-EPP4-U0066-M0001.tar.gz

After that please confirm if the issue remains and if the time on the server is correct from "Appliance > System Maintenance".

Kind regards
